title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1989-09-29
description:
Set 1

Let The Good Times Roll, Feel Like A Stranger, Franklin's Tower, Wang Dang Doodle, Jack A Roe, Memphis Blues, We Can Run But We Can't Hide, Bird Song, Promised Land

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Blow Away*, Playin' In The Band-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Death Don't Have No Mercy-> Sugar Magnolia, E: The Mighty Quinn

Last 'Death Don't Have No Mercy' 3/21/70 Early [1334]
